493" class="node node-recipe node-carousel-slide-narrow clearfix"><div class="vertical-push-item__image"> <img src="//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/styles/carousel_small/public/recipe_images/recipe-image-legacy-id--9401_12.jpg?itok=ro8sV2V-" width="324" height="294" alt="Kale pasta with chilli &amp; anchovy" title="Kale pasta with chilli &amp; anchovy" /></div><h3 class="vertical-push-item__title"> <a href="/recipes/5842/kale-pasta-with-chilli-and-anchovy"> Kale pasta with chilli &amp; anchovy </a></h3><div class="push-item__ratings"><div class="clearfix fivestar-average-stars fivestar-average-text"><div class="fivestar-static-form-item"><div class="form-item form-type-item"><div class="field-main"><div class="fivestar-bbcgoodfood"><div class="clearfix fivestar-widget-static fivestar-widget-static-vote fivestar-widget-static-5"><div class="star star-1 star-odd star-first"><span class="on">4.416665</span></div><div class="star star-2 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-3 star-odd"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-4 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-5 star-odd star-last"><span class="off"></span></div></div></div></div><div class="description"><p class="fivestar-summary fivestar-summary-">(21 <span class="rating-text"> ratings</span>)</p></div></div></div></div></div> </article></li><li class=""><article id="node-93639" class="node node-recipe node-carousel-slide-narrow clearfix"><div class="vertical-push-item__image"> <img src="//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/styles/carousel_small/public/recipe_images/recipe-image-legacy-id--3050_12.jpg?itok=7B7-iFu7" width="324" height="294" alt="Jewelled cranberry &amp; juniper red cabbage" title="Jewelled cranberry &amp; juniper red cabbage" /></div><h3 class="vertical-push-item__title"> <a href="/recipes/2324/jewelled-cranberry-and-juniper-red-cabbage"> Jewelled cranberry &amp; juniper red cabbage </a></h3><div class="push-item__ratings